  "description": "A panoramic view of a city illuminated by a fiery orange glow, likely from a wildfire, is captured from an elevated position overlooking a landscape of trees and suburban houses. The glow dominates the midground, obscuring details of the city and casting a dramatic light across the scene. Trees in the foreground are silhouetted against the bright light, creating a strong contrast. The scene evokes a sense of danger and scale, highlighting the power of the fire and its impact on the surrounding environment.  The lighting suggests it's dusk or nighttime, and a faint moon or bright star is visible within the orange haze.",
